已经没有人能帮助K

854
01:14:13,96 --> 01:14:15,89
...the people of the world.
这个世界的人们

855
01:14:16,96 --> 01:14:18,99
Not since I...
至少在我K

856
01:14:19,90 --> 01:14:23,03
Father!
父亲！

857
01:15:34,10 --> 01:15:38,69
Listen carefully, my son, for we shall never speak again.
好好听着，吾儿 这将是我们最后一次谈话

858
01:15:40,57 --> 01:15:43,16
If you hear me now...
若你现在听得到我

859
01:15:43,34 --> 01:15:46,36
...then you have made use of the only means left to you:
那你便使用到仅剩的能力之一

860
01:15:47,27 --> 01:15:51,21
The crystal source through which our communications begun.
便是让我们开始沟通的水晶源头

861
01:15:52,18 --> 01:15:54,58
The circle is now complete.
这个过程已然完整

862
01:15:54,95 --> 01:15:58,15
You have made a dreadful mistake, Kal-EI.
凯尔，你犯了极大的罪过

863
01:16:01,56 --> 01:16:05,08
You did this of your own free will...
你以自由意志决定

864
01:16:05,63 --> 01:16:08,42
...in spite of all I could say to dissuade you.
枉顾我尽一切所能想说服你

865
01:16:10,73 --> 01:16:12,32
I...
我K

866
01:16:12,50 --> 01:16:16,99
Now you have returned to me for one last chance to redeem yourself.
现在你回到我面前 最后一次试着证明自己

867
01:16:17,17 --> 01:16:22,07
This too finally I have anticipated, my son.
这部分最后我也预料到了，吾儿

868
01:16:24,75 --> 01:16:26,91
Look at me, Kal-EI.
看着我，凯尔

869
01:16:29,35 --> 01:16:33,95
Once before when you were small, I died...
当你小时候，我曾死过一次

870
01:16:35,19 --> 01:16:38,16
...while giving you a chance for life.
是为了给你生命

871
01:16:39,29 --> 01:16:43,25
And now, even though it will exhaust the final energy left within me...
现在，虽然这将用尽 我体内最后的能量K

872
01:16:43,96 --> 01:16:45,80
Father, no.
父亲，不要

873
01:16:47,30 --> 01:16:49,77
Look at me, Kal-EI.
看着我，凯尔

874
01:16:52,51 --> 01:16:57,31
The Kryptonian prophecy will be at last fulfilled.
氪星的预言终于将被实现

875
01:16:57,61 --> 01:17:03,14
The son becomes the father, the father becomes the son.
儿子变成父亲，父亲化为儿子

876
01:17:07,66 --> 01:17:11,56
Farewell forever, Kal-EI.
永别了，凯尔

877
01:17:14,83 --> 01:17:17,30
Remember me, my son.
要记得我，吾儿

878
01:17:47,33 --> 01:17:48,92
My son.
吾儿

879
01:18:04,51 --> 01:18:06,21
Father!
父亲！

880
01:18:19,86 --> 01:18:23,32
Harold. Coffee, black, no sugar.
哈洛，黑咖啡，不加糖

881
01:18:23,50 --> 01:18:26,59
Black, no sug... Yeah. Yeah.
黑咖啡，不加K

882
01:18:27,47 --> 01:18:29,03
Who's paying, huh?
谁付钱啊？

883
01:18:30,07 --> 01:18:32,80
No, no! There's three of them. That cockamamie general...
不，那里有三个人 有荒谬的将军

884
01:18:32,97 --> 01:18:37,10
...and a big truck with hair on it and a broad that looks like the queen of the runway.
一台长头发的大卡车 和像伸展台皇后的女人

885
01:18:37,28 --> 01:18:42,01
They can fly, they can see through things. Anything Superman can do, they can do.
他们能飞，能透视 超人能做的，他们都办得到

886
01:18:42,48 --> 01:18:44,78
Where is he, anyway?
他人呢？

887
01:18:44,99 --> 01:18:46,98
Maybe he hasn't heard about it yet, chief.
也许他还没有听到消息，老编

888
01:18:47,15 --> 01:18:49,32
- Maybe... - Maybe he's just run out of guts.
-或许K -或许他的胆量用完了

889
01:18:49,49 --> 01:18:52,12
- No sugar. And don't call me "chief." - He'll be here.
-不加糖，而且别叫我老编 -他会来的

890
01:18:52,29 --> 01:18:55,82
- Lf there's any way at all, he'll be here. - Yeah, he'll be here.
-如果他有办法他一定会来的 -没错，他一定会来的

891
01:18:58,37 --> 01:19:00,63
- What's going on? - I don't know.
-现在怎么样了？ -我不知道

892
01:19:01,34 --> 01:19:03,24
- Hey, Charlie, you feel that? - Yeah.
-你感觉到了吗，查理？ -有

893
01:19:03,54 --> 01:19:04,94
Sounds like an earthquake.
感觉好像地震

894
01:19:07,04 --> 01:19:08,60
Oh, my!
我的天啊

895
01:19:14,72 --> 01:19:17,38
- It's those three. - Stop!
-就是那三个 -停！

896
01:19:17,55 --> 01:19:20,85
- Oh, my God, they're here now! - Oh, no!
-天啊，他们已经来了 -不好了

897
01:19:32,43 --> 01:19:33,66
This is scary!
好恐怖

898
01:20:22,75 --> 01:20:24,88
You all right, chief?
你没事吧？老编

899
01:20:25,39 --> 01:20:26,79
Hi.
嗨！

900
01:20:28,72 --> 01:20:31,62
You should see the White House. They'll be cleaning for months.
你们该看看白宫 得好几个月才能清干净

901
01:20:31,79 --> 01:20:33,12
Lex Luthor.
我是雷克斯路瑟

902
01:20:33,69 --> 01:20:34,92
Wouldn't you know it?
你猜不到吧？

903
01:20:35,56 --> 01:20:38,40
This is the son of Jor-EI?
这是乔尔的儿子？

904
01:20:38,57 --> 01:20:40,47
- No, but I bet you're a son of a... - Jimmy!
-不，但你一定是个K -吉姆！

905
01:20:41,70 --> 01:20:44,69
You promised me the son of Jor-EI.
你答应给我乔尔的儿子

906
01:20:46,17 --> 01:20:47,33
Yes, Your Grace.
没错，阁下

907
01:20:47,94 --> 01:20:51,54
But what I've given you is the next best thing.
但是K 我所给你的是次好的

908
01:20:51,71 --> 01:20:54,74
You just hold on to that little lady, and he'll be along.
抓住那位小姐K 他一定会来K

909
01:20:54,92 --> 01:20:56,47
See, they have this relationship.
他们有这种特殊关系

910
01:20:56,65 --> 01:21:00,98
She does all his public relations, and he gives her every exclusive.
她替他做公共关系 而他给她所有独家新闻

911
01:21:01,16 --> 01:21:03,82
They're the best of friends. You know what I mean?
他们是最好的朋友 了解我的意思吗？

912
01:21:04,16 --> 01:21:07,39
What an undemanding male this Superman must be.
这个超人还真随便

913
01:21:07,83 --> 01:21:10,46
You could use a tuck here and there yourself, sister.
你也需要改进一点

914
01:21:10,96 --> 01:21:12,56
Wait!
等一下！

915
01:21:12,73 --> 01:21:14,10
- I'm sorry! - She lives for now.
-对不起！ -她暂时可以活命

916
01:21:15,04 --> 01:21:17,40
Kill the rest, starting with him.
把其他人都杀了 就从他开始

917
01:21:19,94 --> 01:21:22,43
Wait. Wait, wait, wait!
等等K

918
01:21:22,61 --> 01:21:24,17
Wait. Wait.
等一下！等一下！

919
01:21:24,34 --> 01:21:28,44
Don't you remember the White House? The Oval Room? We had a few laughs there.
还记得白宫吗？椭圆形办公室 我们曾有过欢笑

920
01:21:29,02 --> 01:21:30,57
You ought to have that fixed.
你们一定要改一改

921
01:21:30,78 --> 01:21:32,68
（白宫投降）

922
01:21:42,16 --> 01:21:43,36
General...
将军

923
01:21:44,26 --> 01:21:46,39
...haven't you heard of freedom of the press?
没听过媒体言论自由吗？

924
01:21:46,60 --> 01:21:48,63
- Superman! - Superman, thank God.
-超人！ -感谢老天，是超人

925
01:21:49,60 --> 01:21:50,97
I mean, get him!
我叫你去抓他！

926
01:21:51,37 --> 01:21:53,20
Come to me, son of Jor-EI!
到我面前来，乔尔之子

927
01:21:53,71 --> 01:21:56,54
Kneel before Zod!
到查德面前下跪

928
01:22:11,16 --> 01:22:13,15
Watch out. You all right?
小心！你没事吧？

929
01:22:17,33 --> 01:22:19,20
（白派瑞 总编辑）

930
01:22:32,75 --> 01:22:34,30
Son of Jor-EI.
乔尔之子

931
01:22:34,78 --> 01:22:37,34
We were beginning to think you were a coward.
我们开始以为你是个懦夫

932
01:22:37,72 --> 01:22:38,98
I'm not a coward, Zod.
我不是懦夫，查德

933
01:22:39,25 --> 01:22:42,31
It is extremely likely you are merely a fool.
你八成只是个笨蛋

934
01:22:42,49 --> 01:22:44,86
Like father, like son.
有其父必有其子

935
01:23:01,14 --> 01:23:02,54
Look out!
小心

936
01:23:05,61 --> 01:23:08,38
Then die as you deserve to!
你该死就得死！

937
01:23:18,53 --> 01:23:20,72
Come on, come on, Superman! Get him!
快！抓住他！

938
01:23:20,99 --> 01:23:23,05
Man, this is gonna be good.
一定会没事的

939
01:23:59,07 --> 01:24:00,66
Superman.
超人

940
01:24:21,69 --> 01:24:24,05
- Hey, that's the chief's. - The chief's got it.
-那是老编的 -老编已经有了

941
01:24:32,77 --> 01:24:34,73
What, you hit a woman?
什么，你打了女人？

942
01:24:57,86 --> 01:25:01,02
Oh, my God! My baby!
天啊，我的小孩！

943
01:25:01,40 --> 01:25:03,83
Help my baby!
救救我的宝贝

944
01:25:06,70 --> 01:25:08,40
Thank you.
哦？谢谢

945
01:25:09,97 --> 01:25:13,53
This Superman is nothing of the kind.
这个超人没什么了不起

946
01:25:13,74 --> 01:25:16,14
- I've discovered his weakness. - Yes.
我已经发现他的弱点了 -是啊

947
01:25:16,31 --> 01:25:17,71
He cares.
他关心

948
01:25:17,98 --> 01:25:21,24
He actually cares for these Earth people.
他真的很关心地球人

949
01:25:21,42 --> 01:25:24,58
- Like pets? - I suppose so.
-就像宠物一样？ -我想是吧！

950
01:25:32,76 --> 01:25:34,66
I'll draw his fire...
我来分散他的注意力

951
01:25:34,83 --> 01:25:36,76
...with some of my own.
用我自己的力量

952
01:26:04,32 --> 01:26:05,99
What's happening to those cars?
那些车子怎么了？

953
01:26:09,43 --> 01:26:10,90
Get out of the way!
别挡路！

954
01:26:28,68 --> 01:26:30,38
（冷静一下！）

955
01:27:26,07 --> 01:27:27,17
Superman.
超人

956
01:28:01,31 --> 01:28:02,47
（请享用可口可乐）

957
01:28:12,72 --> 01:28:14,12
Oh, thank you!
真是谢谢你

958
01:28:14,29 --> 01:28:16,85
I never thought this thing would go the distance.
我没想到这事会持续这么久

959
01:28:31,07 --> 01:28:33,16
No! Don't do it!
不要！别动手！

960
01:28:33,61 --> 01:28:35,27
The people!
车上的人！

961
01:28:39,91 --> 01:28:41,71
Throw it!
丢啊！

962
01:29:02,94 --> 01:29:06,24
- Get away from there. Get away from there. - Let's help them out!
-别靠近那里，远离那个地方 -我们快去帮他们

963
01:29:09,78 --> 01:29:13,23
- I got her. I got her. Don't worry. - He's dead.
-别担心，我去救她 -他死了

964
01:29:14,88 --> 01:29:16,87
Superman is dead.
超人死了

965
01:29:20,12 --> 01:29:21,38
They've killed Superman.
他们杀了超人

966
01:29:22,82 --> 01:29:25,12
- He's dead. - Let's go get them!
-他死了 -我们去找他们报仇

967
01:29:25,29 --> 01:29:27,89
- Come on, we'll show them! - I know some judo. Let's go!
-来，让他们知道我们的厉害 -我会空手道，上啊！

968
01:29:28,43 --> 01:29:29,95
Come on!
来吧

969
01:30:00,39 --> 01:30:03,02
I'm holding it, I'm holding it!
我抓住了！我抓住了！

970
01:30:03,20 --> 01:30:05,60
What can you do if you can't see what's happening?
什么都看不到能做什么？

971
01:30:10,57 --> 01:30:13,70
- Hold on! - Oh, my God!
-抓稳了 -天啊！

972
01:30:16,28 --> 01:30:18,77
（不准进入）

973
01:30:21,31 --> 01:30:23,44
（准备下地狱吧！ 世界末日到了！）

974
01:31:22,61 --> 01:31:25,08
You can't leave us!
你不能丢下我们

975
01:31:29,78 --> 01:31:34,08
So he is a coward after all.
那么，他毕竟是个懦夫

976
01:31:34,49 --> 01:31:36,01
He's gone.
他走了

977
01:31:36,19 --> 01:31:37,71
Come back, Superman!
回来！超人

978
01:31:42,80 --> 01:31:44,46
Don't leave us!
别丢下我们！

979
01:31:47,37 --> 01:31:49,36
He chickened out.
他临阵逃脱了

980
01:31:49,87 --> 01:31:50,93
Phony!
骗子！

981
01:31:52,27 --> 01:31:54,21
Superman didn't even do nothing.
超人什么都没做

982
01:31:54,47 --> 01:31:56,60
Come on, let's go.
我们走

983
01:32:03,62 --> 01:32:07,42
- There they are. - Get away from here. Jimmy.
-他们在那儿 -快走开，吉姆

984
01:32:16,43 --> 01:32:18,26
Our victory is complete.
我们已经战胜了

985
01:32:18,43 --> 01:32:20,19
The son of Jor-El has fled.
乔尔之子逃跑了

986
01:32:20,37 --> 01:32:23,06
- Superman fled? - I don't believe you.
-超人跑掉了？ -我不相信你

987
01:32:23,24 --> 01:32:27,30
You heard him. Three against one, you should've taken two ears and a tail.
你听到了，三对一 你大获全胜

988
01:32:27,47 --> 01:32:30,57
- He fled in fear of us. - He'll be back.
-他被我们吓走了 -他会回来的

989
01:32:30,74 --> 01:32:33,11
As long as he's alive, he's gonna try again.
只要他还活着，就会再试一次

990
01:32:33,28 --> 01:32:36,72
- The next time, we will kill him. - The next time?
-下一次，我们会杀了他 -下一次？

991
01:32:37,75 --> 01:32:39,81
The next time?
下一次？

992
01:32:40,55 --> 01:32:42,65
What am I gonna do with you people?
我该拿你们怎么办？

993
01:32:42,82 --> 01:32:45,42
I held up my end. I delivered you the blue boy.
我在这里等着超人出现

994
01:32:45,59 --> 01:32:47,89
What do I get from my triple threat?
你们三位要如何回报我？

995
01:32:48,06 --> 01:32:52,40
"Bow, yield, kneel." That kind of stuff closes out a town.
“鞠躬，屈膝，下跪” 这种事在这里不管用

996
01:32:53,97 --> 01:32:57,77
Why do you say this to me when you know I will kill you for it?
你为什么这样对我说话？ 你明知我可以因此而杀你

997
01:32:57,97 --> 01:33:01,77
Kill me? Lex Luthor?
杀我？雷克斯路瑟？

998
01:33:02,21 --> 01:33:04,97
Extinguish the greatest criminal flame of our age?
杀掉本世代最伟大的罪犯

999
01:33:05,15 --> 01:33:09,28
- Eradicate the only man on earth with... - Let me kill him!
-杀掉地球上唯一K -杀了他

1000
01:33:09,75 --> 01:33:11,34
- Superman's address?
超人的地址？

1001
01:33:15,22 --> 01:33:20,56
What more do you want? I can see the greed written on your face.
你还要什么？ 我看到你脸上写满贪婪

1002
01:33:20,73 --> 01:33:23,59
A small incentive, O Fullest One.
一个小奖励，最棒的

1003
01:33:23,76 --> 01:33:26,79
A mere bauble to jog the memory.
一样挑起回忆的小东西

1004
01:33:27,40 --> 01:33:28,59
What more?
还要什么？

1005
01:33:29,57 --> 01:33:30,76
Cuba.
古巴

1006
01:33:38,78 --> 01:33:45,01
I trust you are not wasting my time, Lex Luthor.
雷克斯路瑟 希望你不是在浪费我的时间

1007
01:33:45,22 --> 01:33:47,45
Of course not, Your Turbulence.
当然不是，难搞的大人

1008
01:34:33,63 --> 01:34:35,73
Show yourself, coward!
现身吧，懦夫

1009
01:34:38,64 --> 01:34:40,83
Son of a coward!
懦夫的儿子

1010
01:34:47,21 --> 01:34:48,51
I'm here, Zod.
我在这里，查德

1011
01:34:48,92 --> 01:34:51,94
- Let Miss Lane go, step inside. We'll talk. - No, don't, Superman!
-放莲恩小姐走，我们到里面谈谈 -不要，超人

1012
01:34:52,12 --> 01:34:54,09
Please don't listen to him. He's just...
别听他的，他只是个K

1013
01:34:54,52 --> 01:34:55,78
Stop.
停手

1014
01:34:55,96 --> 01:34:57,95
Your powers are identical to mine.
你的能力与我的相同

1015
01:34:58,12 --> 01:35:01,36
But we are three. We could tear you limb from limb.
但我们有三个人 可以把你五马分尸

1016
01:35:01,66 --> 01:35:02,89
Do it, Your Grace.
下手吧，将军大人

1017
01:35:03,26 --> 01:35:05,42
Just grab a leg and just make a wish.
抱只腿，许个愿

1018
01:35:06,93 --> 01:35:09,33
But you are victim to another fatal weakness...
但你是另一项致命弱点的受害者

1019
01:35:09,77 --> 01:35:11,20
...your compassion.
就是你的同情心

1020
01:35:11,37 --> 01:35:13,84
The death of others means more to you than your own.
对你来说 他人的死比你自己的更重要

1021
01:35:14,01 --> 01:35:15,47
Yes, with rare exceptions.
是的，但偶有例外

1022
01:35:15,91 --> 01:35:21,44
Your father condemned us to an eternal living death. Your fate will be the same.
你父亲让我们进人间炼狱永不得翻身 你的命运也将相同

1023
01:35:21,71 --> 01:35:23,77
You will live, Kal-EI, forever...
凯尔，你将永远活着

1024
01:35:23,95 --> 01:35:28,94
...as my slave. If not, then others will pay for your obstinate attitude.
做我的奴隶 否则他人将为你的固执付出代价

1025
01:35:29,12 --> 01:35:34,65
Innocent people, millions if necessary, beginning with this Lois person.
无辜的人，必要时可达上百万 就从这位露薏丝开始

1026
01:35:34,83 --> 01:35:36,45
- Don't, Superman, don't! - Stop it!
-超人，不要 -停手

1027
01:35:40,67 --> 01:35:42,90
All right, Zod.
好吧，查德

1028
01:35:43,57 --> 01:35:45,00
It's over.
一切都结束了

1029
01:35:47,84 --> 01:35:51,61
Your Grace, don't believe him! You don't know him the way that I do.
将军大人，别相信他 你不像我如此了解他

1030
01:35:53,81 --> 01:35:56,01
I sense the presence of Jor-El here.
